00:29:33.000 --> 00:29:35.910
and about to come in
the next few years.

00:29:35.910 --> 00:29:39.750
We are looking at some
amazing disruption

00:29:39.750 --> 00:29:42.000
can happen in this market.

00:29:42.000 --> 00:29:47.040
You can think about, imagine
