network that we have at BRAC,

00:31:08.190 --> 00:31:09.930
real magic can happen
in the coming days

00:31:09.930 --> 00:31:11.730
and real disruption can happen.

00:31:11.730 --> 00:31:16.440
And personally speaking
over the last few years.

00:31:16.440 --> 00:31:19.380
As I have learned to
